Program: Omnibus
Title: The Donner Party
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lhb
Last Broadcast Date: 24 June 1997
In 1846 George Donner led a wagon train trek of people across the USA to start a new life in California with as much land as they wanted. Of the 87 members of the party only 48 survived to reach their destination.